{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f0c366e5ae","title":"关于没收汉奸财产问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d82cccc4eb","index":0,"year":1937,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"f0c366e5ae"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji2","name":"毛泽东文集第二卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji2":{"comments":[{"id":"72c4998d7f","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"f0c366e5ae","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据中央档案馆保存的抄件刊印。"},{"id":"b70cd6c333","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"f0c366e5ae","index":1,"part_index":1,"offset":5,"text":"朱，指朱德。彭，指彭德怀，当时任八路军副总司令。任，指任弼时，当时任八路军政治部主任。"},{"id":"d625f8781c","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"f0c366e5ae","index":2,"part_index":3,"offset":1,"text":"洛，指洛甫，即张闻天，当时任中共中央政治局常委，在中央负总责。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a1d15b9852","type":"title","text":"关于没收汉奸财产问题","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"f0c366e5ae"},{"id":"b70cd6c333","type":"appellation","text":"朱、彭、任：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"f0c366e5ae"},{"id":"d625f8781c","type":"paragraph","text":"十一日电悉。没收大地主，指没收汉奸政策的主要阶级内容，大地主而未为汉奸者，当然不在没收之列。在一切汉奸分子中，首先应坚决没收大地主，而对中层分子之为汉奸者，在未得民众同意以前，不应急于没收。工农中有被迫为汉奸者，应取宽大政策，以说服教育为主。这是统一战线中的阶级路线，有向全体明确说明的必要。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"f0c366e5ae"},{"id":"420320958f","type":"paragraph","text":"洛、毛","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"f0c366e5ae"}],"page":{"id":"2081c74626","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"f0c366e5ae","start":54,"end":54}}}},"__N_SSG":true}